description._content: Description: Aleppo Pine - Pinus balepensis, average age about 55 years, Adelphi Forest, between Kannavia and Yerokamina Valleys, Elevation 1,800 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Description: Aleppo Pine - Pinus halepensis, 50 years old to the west of Kapoura Forest Station, Adelphi Forest, Elevation about 1,800 feet. Location: Cyprus Date: 1920-1939 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/698 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
